bringViewToTop

public static ReviewTableView bringViewToTop()
Brings the code review view to the top no matter when review view is closed or not. Means that it is opened if it has not been opened yet, or it is brought to top if it already has been opened, but not brought to top.

Returns:
the ReviewTableView instance to be opened and/or bright to top.

getActiveView

public static ReviewTableView getActiveView()
Provides the active view of the Review table view. This active review table view associates with the active window. Returns null if there is no active review table view in the active window.

Returns:
the active review editor view. Returns null if there is no active review table view in the active window.

getViews

public static ReviewTableView[] getViews()
Provides the array of the Review table view. A review table view in the array associates with the opened window. The array might contain null if there is no active review table view in the active window.

Returns:
the array of the review table views.

Closes the opened code review view if it's opened.
